    <item>
      <title>“无法交易”：剧烈波动扰乱巴西掉期利率市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/-it-s-untradeable-wild-swings-roil-brazil-swap-rates-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于押注较低掉期利率的投资者来说，巴西应该是天堂。由于实际利率高得惊人，且通胀率正在下降，从利率下降中获利的交易是理所当然的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/-it-s-untradeable-wild-swings-roil-brazil-swap-rates-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 14:40:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国消费者信心指数跌至七个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-14/us-consumer-sentiment-drops-to-seven-month-low-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[密歇根大学信心指数 6 月份从 69.1 降至 65.6。彭博社对经济学家的调查中值预测该指数将升至 72。Mike McKee 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-14/us-consumer-sentiment-drops-to-seven-month-low-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 14:28:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
